                                                            Diagram point of view
                                                            =====================
                                          
                                          
                                          =====================================================================
                                          Set-1:: intermediate operations(will return streams)
                                          =====================================================================
                                          
                                          Filters ==== >filter()
                                          mapping ====> map() & flatMap()
                                          slicing =====> distinct() & limit() & skip()
                                          
                                          
                                          =====================================================================
                                          Set-2 :: Terminal OPerations (will return results)
                                          =====================================================================
                                          
                                          Finding ===> findFirst() & findAny()
                                          Matching ==> anyMatch()  & allMatch() & noneMatch()
                                          Collection ==>   collect()
                                          






































































